uefi-hv-bypass
==============

Third-party attribution.

Ophion/
-------
Originally derived from https://github.com/zer0condition/Ophion (MIT-style
license preserved in Ophion/LICENSE). Imported via the amaralkaff/Ophion fork
at commit 7b501992bd71af7f5330ec697a1cbe27921157f9 plus local divergence
covering: xhunter1 hook integration, VMM logger, EPT cloak (Phase 7d), and the
UEFI VMM port hooks consumed by MongilLoader/OphionDxe.

Going forward, driver source under Ophion/ is maintained directly in this
repository alongside MongilLoader/OphionDxe so that VMCALL ABI changes
(MongilLoader/include/OphionAbi.h <-> Ophion/include/hv_types.h) land in a
single atomic commit.

EfiGuard
--------
Pre-built binaries under .tools/EfiGuard-v1.4 are unmodified releases from
https://github.com/Mattiwatti/EfiGuard, used at boot for PatchGuard and DSE
bypass. Source not redistributed; see upstream for license.

EDK II
------
The edk2/ tree is gitignored and provided locally as the UEFI build
environment. See https://github.com/tianocore/edk2 for license.
